Title: Part 1: Lets go on an Adventure!
Text:
Sauron is back, and with him is the One Ring.

It cannot stay in the Shire!

Meet with Gandalf in Bree to discuss further!

But beware of the Black Riders!

They are drawn to the power of the ring!
CompleteText:
"This is the inn Gandalf spoke of.

But he doesn't seem to be here!

Has something happened to him?

Otherwise he is always on time!"( Someone is watching you from the corner of the room !)
